    "\n",
    "  <b>Model Diagnostic Plots – Interpretation</b><br><br>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <b>1. Standardized Residual Plot</b><br>\n",
    "  This plot shows the standardized residuals of the model error term.\n",
    "  The residuals are centered around zero and remain within the ±2 range,\n",
